  <section name="site-info">
    <h3>Site Information</h3>
    <p>This site is a Ruby on Rails app, tracked by a git repository that is deployed to Heroku. The database is PostgreSQL and is also hosted on Heroku. The domain name is registered with Namecheap. All of the photo albums and photos come from Flickr.</p>
    
    <p>Login information for these services can be found in the "Account Logins" tab.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section name="articles">
    <h3>Posting Articles</h3>
    <p>In order to post news articles, go to the News section and click the "New Article" button in the top right. If you aren't logged in, you will need to do so by visiting the Member Zone or clicking the "Admin Login" that will appear in place of the "New Article" button. Fill out all the title, author, and text fields, then submit your post.</p>
    
    <h3>Managing Articles</h3>
    <p>Articles can be edited or deleted via buttons in the individual article pages if you are logged in.</p>
    
    <h3>Managing Comments</h3>
    <p>Comments on posts can be deleted from the individual article page if you are logged in.</p>
  </section>
  
